Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:35.09,0:01:38.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了找尋在第二界層\N某一處的真實之鏡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:38.58,0:01:40.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們來到了十字鎮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.46,0:01:45.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然我們拯救了\N被東傑拉拉支配的市民
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.56,0:01:49.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但要令著日夜顛倒的市鎮\N恢復真正的和平
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.68,0:01:52.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還是需要真實之鏡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.66,0:01:56.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好!\N我一定會找到的!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.27,0:01:59.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天也會是又有趣又有型呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.40,0:02:07.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第九話\N嚇一跳!\N世紀大發明鏡子探測機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.67,0:02:19.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要製造真實之鏡探測機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.48,0:02:22.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真簡單,對我來說毫無難處
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.08,0:02:45.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,完成了!\N爆炸是成功之母!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.06,0:02:56.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好慢啊!渡,認真地跑啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.58,0:02:59.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我…已不行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.01,0:03:06.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,師傅…不要再幹這種事…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.73,0:03:09.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快點去找真實之鏡吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.64,0:03:12.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蠢材!\N不論什麼時候也要繼續修煉才是武士啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.05,0:03:14.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對啊,對啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.52,0:03:18.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟著會更加嚴格啊\N火美子,來下一個吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.18,0:03:34.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好!火美子,上吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.41,0:03:39.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,天真!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.96,0:03:49.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好痛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.78,0:03:52.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真沒用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.18,0:03:55.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡!\N不可以用眼去追看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.52,0:03:57.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要打開心眼!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.45,0:03:59.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,心眼?\N近視?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.09,0:04:02.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是心眼!心中的眼睛!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.75,0:04:05.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太多的東西\N沒可能用眼睛全部看見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.30,0:04:08.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想看又看不見時便會心慌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.70,0:04:10.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,越心慌便會越看不見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.55,0:04:14.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那不如索性\N閉起眼睛集中精神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.51,0:04:16.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣的話便會感到氣勢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.30,0:04:17.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全部的東西也能看得見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.88,0:04:20.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這便叫做打開心眼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.38,0:04:23.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妖怪啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.43,0:04:25.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,誰是妖怪啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.48,0:04:27.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?還活著的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.68,0:04:29.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們在這裏幹什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.13,0:04:32.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們是為了\N找真實之鏡而來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.54,0:04:34.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真實之鏡?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.23,0:04:36.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,婆婆,你知道嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.87,0:04:42.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不,我才不知道\N倒是…要吃這個嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.70,0:04:44.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嘩!是圓子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.47,0:04:46.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來,不用客氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.53,0:04:50.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我剛剛想吃甜食呢\N這個好像很好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.02,0:04:51.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.17,0:04:53.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不客氣了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.56,0:04:56.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好好吃啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.80,0:05:01.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好辣!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.95,0:05:02.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,水啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.40,0:05:06.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,水…水啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.74,0:05:10.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雲?\N水在哪裏?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.17,0:05:12.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼要喝水?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.87,0:05:15.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你吃了那麼辣的東西\N也沒事嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.22,0:05:16.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很好吃啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.58,0:05:18.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,水啊!我要找水!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.70,0:05:20.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.27,0:05:25.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,誰會把這麼重要的真實之鏡\N交給他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.94,0:05:32.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哪裏有水啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.56,0:05:35.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真奇怪呢,這裏應該是湖啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.35,0:05:39.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快想辦法啊,口要燒著了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.48,0:05:40.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.11,0:05:47.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很…很可愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.95,0:05:51.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小姐,我口內發生火警\N很對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.43,0:05:54.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果你肯把那水壺的水給我\N我會很感謝你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.28,0:05:56.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.71,0:05:58.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是感激不盡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.97,0:05:59.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.84,0:06:05.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在這附近水會全部向上流的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.49,0:06:06.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.96,0:06:13.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.25,0:06:15.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,水浮在天空呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.36,0:06:18.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是這個湖的湖水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.81,0:06:20.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.25,0:06:24.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在這附近水是非常珍貴的\N你要好好珍惜啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.20,0:06:26.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.47,0:06:32.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是為什麼\N在口內會發生火警呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.39,0:06:37.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一個奇怪的婆婆\N請我們吃了很辣的圓子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.87,0:06:40.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是蜜婆婆呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.79,0:06:42.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡,怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.60,0:06:54.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我還以為會死掉呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.91,0:06:55.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真蠢材
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.84,0:07:00.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這種小事便暈到\N你還是修煉不足呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.39,0:07:01.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奇怪的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.94,0:07:05.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我叫小桃,請問你是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.91,0:07:10.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我叫渡,是為了找真實之鏡\N而來到這個鎮的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.44,0:07:13.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真實之鏡?我曾經聽過呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.56,0:07:15.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽過?從誰人口中?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.82,0:07:24.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?\N你知道了真實之鏡的所在地?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.95,0:07:28.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對,而且渡他們已經出發了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.26,0:07:33.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣非常糟啊\N不可以把真實之鏡交給他們!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.19,0:07:36.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要這麼激動\N雖然知道了所在地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.50,0:07:39.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但地方很廣闊\N不是那麼容易便找到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.04,0:07:43.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在他們找到之前\N我們先找出來…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.87,0:07:51.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.92,0:08:02.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,完成了…\N真實之鏡探測機已完成了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.78,0:08:04.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,反轉博士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.48,0:08:05.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?那是真的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.23,0:08:11.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對我這天才科學家\N反轉博士來說這只是小兒科
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.73,0:08:13.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且順便已把這部法蘭擎改造了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.96,0:08:19.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已變成了有力量\N足以消滅龍神丸的強力魔神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.04,0:08:21.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有什麼地方不同了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.48,0:08:22.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真蠢材,你看清楚吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.27,0:08:26.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,之前用"鈑手"\N今次是轉槍啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.69,0:08:32.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不只這樣…\N其實這部法蘭擎已裝備了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.83,0:08:35.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以勝過龍神丸的部件了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.53,0:08:37.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.75,0:08:39.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是呢…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.21,0:08:41.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.03,0:08:44.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,秘密!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.94,0:08:49.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼你說\N那完成了的探測機呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.86,0:08:51.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是就在眼前嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.72,0:08:52.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,眼前?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.84,0:08:58.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?好噁心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.48,0:09:01.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個眼球正是偉大的發明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.97,0:09:05.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,本世紀的奇跡\N真實之鏡探測機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.63,0:09:06.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們看看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.09,0:09:12.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,法蘭擎\N這塊是真實之鏡嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.14,0:09:14.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.15,0:09:15.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.55,0:09:19.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是真的時候會說\N[是這個了],很驚訝吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.00,0:09:21.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,誰會驚訝啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.77,0:09:26.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總之這個眼球指向的方向\N便是真實之鏡的所在地了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.38,0:09:28.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我立即開動它,你們等我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.05,0:09:32.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好!立即前進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.25,0:09:38.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂!那邊是牆壁啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.66,0:09:43.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,法蘭擎發現目標後\N只會直線前進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.96,0:09:58.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從消息中的確是那個方向呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.48,0:09:59.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒問題嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.10,0:10:01.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總之我也去看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.43,0:10:08.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?那是真的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.86,0:10:10.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要有真實之鏡的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.40,0:10:13.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,便可以令這第二界層\N恢復原狀嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.38,0:10:13.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.26,0:10:16.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是…那東西真的可以…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.87,0:10:17.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下雨了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.01,0:10:23.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下雨!下雨!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.31,0:10:24.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在做什麼呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.82,0:10:29.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在收集雨水\N這裏一星期只會下一次雨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.13,0:10:32.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以便這樣收集雨水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.97,0:10:34.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是大事件呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.89,0:10:36.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們也幫手吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.66,0:10:42.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,水不夠嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.65,0:10:48.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊,如果湖水恢復了原狀\N便不用這麼辛苦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.79,0:10:50.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要有真實之鏡便行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.98,0:10:53.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是呢\N可是怎樣也不能相信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.96,0:10:55.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.63,0:10:58.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不,因為自從蜜婆婆\N得到了那塊鏡之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.73,0:11:00.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,便變成了一個\N愛作弄人的婆婆呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.82,0:11:03.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鳥先生!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.29,0:11:05.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,古拿瑪!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.26,0:11:07.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這隻鳥是你們的朋友嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.53,0:11:09.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不是鳥!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.16,0:11:10.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鳥兒、鳥兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.12,0:11:11.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,收聲!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.86,0:11:15.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你可以把真實之鏡的事\N再詳細點告訴我嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.89,0:11:20.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很久以前便傳說\N這湖裏有真實之鏡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.43,0:11:24.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要得到它的人\N便能得到幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.87,0:11:28.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是自從多惡達\N來到這個世界之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.00,0:11:31.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,村內的水全都飛到天上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.41,0:11:33.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,村內的人因缺水而很煩惱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.95,0:11:37.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,之後失去了水的湖\N剩下一塊鏡子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.56,0:11:40.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蜜婆婆撿到了它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.59,0:11:45.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,之後蜜婆婆便變成了\N很有精力愛作弄人的婆婆了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.46,0:11:50.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是如此,我想到\N得到了真實之鏡的蜜婆婆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.17,0:11:52.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那樣便叫做幸福嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.47,0:11:53.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就這回事嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.80,0:11:56.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總之我們找蜜婆婆把事情說清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.76,0:11:58.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把鏡子借來用吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.98,0:12:24.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是這個了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.19,0:12:31.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是那個了,是真實之鏡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.72,0:12:40.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我真是美麗\N何時看也是這麼迷人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.23,0:12:46.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.37,0:12:50.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老太婆,把鏡子交給我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.26,0:12:52.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?\N你是誰?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.04,0:12:57.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是誰也好\N不聽我說沒有好下場啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.43,0:13:01.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果這樣我也說不行\N你會怎樣做?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.55,0:13:05.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那便會這樣!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.22,0:13:10.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不錯呢,老太婆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.58,0:13:14.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎樣?這樣也能\N叫我把鏡子交給你嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.48,0:13:18.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當然!法蘭擎2號\N捉住那老太婆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.44,0:13:22.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你想幹什麼?你這色鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.19,0:13:26.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要,要吃我也不好吃啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.71,0:13:31.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂!還給我,那是我的鏡子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.10,0:13:33.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去吧!奇怪珠攻擊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.40,0:13:39.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,接住!接住!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.19,0:13:43.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,接得好,火美子\N反轉博士!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.64,0:13:46.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我已來了\N真實之鏡是不會交給你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.53,0:13:54.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我等你很久了,小子\N但之前要取得真實之鏡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.44,0:13:55.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂!小女孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.75,0:13:57.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我叫火美子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.54,0:14:00.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,玩兵捉賊吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.44,0:14:02.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小蛋!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.74,0:14:12.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小蛋?\N竟變出這樣的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.15,0:14:20.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各位還記得嗎?\N小蛋是反轉博士製造的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.71,0:14:24.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也就是說反轉博士\N是小蛋的生父
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.06,0:14:26.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爸爸!\N兒子!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.16,0:14:29.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真令人感動呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.09,0:14:37.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣的東西對法蘭擎2號來說\N便和水一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.41,0:14:40.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好!趁現在…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.98,0:14:44.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,龍神丸!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.63,0:15:27.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好!來吧!反轉博士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.26,0:15:32.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,出來了嗎?\N廢鐵機械人,法蘭擎2號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.18,0:15:35.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把你真正的恐怖\N解放的時刻到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.55,0:15:38.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓那廢鐵機械人\N見識你的可怕吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.56,0:15:43.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很多謝你惠顧(關西話)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.61,0:15:48.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多謝!多謝!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.98,0:15:52.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你服輸了吧?\N話也說不出來了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.65,0:15:57.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是位於第一界層的\N極西的關西村用的語言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.52,0:15:59.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎樣?龍神丸\N你懂得說嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.95,0:16:02.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,覺得輸了的話便老實投降吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.69,0:16:06.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣的事嚇不到我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.71,0:16:11.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,"你知道嗎?"\N這是第二界層的名古屋市的語言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.10,0:16:16.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,"還想聽嗎"\N這是第四界層箱根村的語言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.99,0:16:19.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,"你沒聽過這樣的說話吧"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.47,0:16:23.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這也是第四界層的京都市語言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.39,0:16:28.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你還想聽哪個地方的方言?\N隨便點吧,來吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.83,0:16:34.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,成功了,龍神丸真厲害!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.12,0:16:36.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣有什麼厲害!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.84,0:16:39.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能說這麼多話有什麼作為?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.01,0:16:43.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡!鏡子怎樣也無所謂了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.10,0:16:45.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要把它打得支離破碎!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.05,0:16:50.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,龍神丸!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.40,0:16:51.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要示弱,渡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.88,0:16:58.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是危險呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.92,0:17:01.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還是這麼強而有力呢\N不要大意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.11,0:17:06.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒問題,那傢伙取出武器時\N要用很多時間是他的弱點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.26,0:17:09.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好!那麼便全力出擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.81,0:17:10.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去吧!渡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.27,0:17:18.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太天真了,看看這個吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.74,0:17:31.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是弩箭,小心點,龍神丸!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.04,0:17:34.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這樣想吧,可是呢…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.62,0:17:42.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,改良了的不只是"鈑手"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.13,0:17:45.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有我的大發明\N飛來飛去光波
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.56,0:17:54.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,先生,這處很危險\N你快帶她們避開一下比較好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.32,0:17:57.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道了,來,小桃\N火美子也來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.49,0:17:58.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂,火美子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.22,0:18:02.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那塊鏡由我拿吧,交給我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.35,0:18:09.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了?我覺得你拿著\N會有危險才替你拿啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.54,0:18:13.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.79,0:18:17.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好,真是好孩子\N你也快點到那邊躲起來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.40,0:18:19.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我有點事想起要干
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.32,0:18:21.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.51,0:18:31.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,活該!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.21,0:18:34.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個光球\N到底是從何處飛來的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.72,0:18:38.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在幹什麼?渡\N這樣也是在下的徒弟嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.09,0:18:40.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要幹勁和拼勁!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.40,0:18:44.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼辦?龍神丸\N我不知道它會從何處攻來啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.47,0:18:45.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂!龍神丸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.12,0:18:47.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要焦急,渡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.69,0:18:50.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用眼觀看的話\N看不見的東西卻會跑出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.71,0:18:52.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用心眼去看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.08,0:18:55.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,心眼?說起來…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.67,0:18:58.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可以用眼睛追看\N要打開心眼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.33,0:19:01.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,心眼…是嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.26,0:19:09.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,後面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.01,0:19:12.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很好,渡,是這樣了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.63,0:19:21.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看見了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.67,0:19:24.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看見了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.31,0:19:27.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我看到了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.38,0:19:31.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他擋到了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.65,0:19:33.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,成功了,渡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.16,0:19:39.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,加油!龍神丸!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.63,0:19:54.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是機會了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.24,0:19:59.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,必殺!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.06,0:20:03.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,登龍劍!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.97,0:20:19.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,成功了!成功了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.07,0:20:22.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,做得很好,渡\N不愧是在下的徒弟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.24,0:20:24.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,萬歲!萬歲!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.11,0:20:30.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.88,0:20:31.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.82,0:20:35.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那傢伙是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.21,0:20:41.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我擔心的走來竟變成這樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.87,0:20:44.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡的龍神丸,受死吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.59,0:20:47.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,危險!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.10,0:20:55.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那便是真實之鏡了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.51,0:20:57.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鏡子啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.37,0:21:11.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要這真實之鏡不再存在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.23,0:21:13.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個第二界層便沒有救了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.95,0:21:21.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真實之鏡破了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.79,0:21:22.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.60,0:21:58.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這麼辛苦才找到…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:58.62,0:22:02.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個世界永遠也無法復原了

